title.label: Best game in the App Store

content.label: I love this!

This game is a first person dungeon crawler. But wait don't wet ur pants with excitement yet! It's a huge disappointment. Very repetitive boring game. Traps are difficult to see because you can't look down so u only see them from the very corner of the screen, very few traps.    Enemies walk in the same path, don't chase you after seeing u, and they're not ranged so u literally have to run in their face to lose 1/3 of ur hp. And even if u somehow get hurt, u can find health kits almost everywhere. Weapons are found every like 15 seconds and u can kill up to 3 guys (or more with perks) per weapon. Most shop upgrades are really dumb ideas, like allowing you to find crossbows from chests, even though there r already bows that can be found. And it's not like crossbows are any stronger than bows because everything is a one shot (except bosses which are super easy and are 3 shotted anyway) Wayyyy too easy. I give them two stars for smooth gameplay (lots of ads and you can't stop moving forward which is really annoying) Also game drains ur battery fast don't waste ur time. Click the back button and move onto the next app.
Really good and fun but watch out for bad guys
